IC: *Inside the woods, Kyla's causing havoc. She's managed to streak right past most of the Hunters (As far as she can tell!) and is picking them off from behind. Some she bites and slashes, others she burns... the trees keep her safe from the worst of the bolts. The men that she manages to scare are driven out of the trees and into the open. Not everything goes her own way though -she's already bleeding in several places.*<br>
